http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Passport-mela-in-Bengaluru-Hubballi-on-Feb.-6/article14013327.ece

The Regional Passport Office, Bengaluru, will hold a ‘Jumbo Passport Mela’ on February 6 at Passport Seva Kendras in Bengaluru, (Lalbagh and Marathahalli) and Hubballi. Regional Passport Office, Bengaluru, in a press release said that 3,800 appointments for normal category for this mela would be released at 4.30 p.m. on February 1. Details can be obtained from the website www.passportindia.gov.in by referring to the second paragraph of the section Passport Mela requirements under Passport Office (Bengaluru).